Package: gephir
Title: R Interface to Gephi Graph Analysis Toolkit
Version: 2.0.0
Authors@R: person("yangr", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "yangr@example.com")
Description: Provides a comprehensive R interface to the Gephi graph analysis toolkit
    via the 'gephi-cli' Python package and 'reticulate'. Supports graph import/export
    (GEXF, GraphML, GML, CSV, etc.), 11 layout algorithms, 15+ metrics, 17 filters,
    11 graph generators, and image/PDF/SVG rendering. Interoperates with 'igraph',
    data.frame, and adjacency matrix objects.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.0
Imports:
    reticulate (>= 1.28)
Suggests:
    igraph,
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
Config/reticulate:
  list(
    packages = list(
      list(package = "gephi-cli", pip = TRUE)
    )
  )
